Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
deselectModule(25.10)                                    deselectModule(25.10)

Name
       deselectModule

Syntax
       deselectModule

        [-help]

       <name>

       Deselects the specified module.

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description that includes type and default infor-
              mation for each deselectModule parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man deselectModule

       <name> Specifies the name of the module to be deselected.

Example
       The following example deselects the DTMF_INST module.

       deselectModule DTMF_INST

Related Information
              * selectModule

